c: 39
v: 23
t: "Issader ed Öebbi ûûam n wawal. Tazmamt, degs acbi, allus. Ad ccirwen segs igwelman akked wulawen n wid ippagwaden Mass nnsen, sinna, igwelman akked wulawen nnsen ad iêninen ar usmekti n Öebbi. D tagi ay d nnhaya n Öebbi. Inehhu yis, win i S ihwan. Win Itlef Öebbi, ur illi wa ara t inhun"